sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Pacman
    participant F as GhostFrightened
    participant G as Ghost
    participant H as GhostHome
    participant GM as GameManager
    participant SM as ScoreManager

    Note over P,G: Ghost is in Frightened state (blue)

    P->>F: OnCollisionEnter2D (Pacman layer)
    F->>F: Eaten()  (eaten = true)
    F->>G: SetPosition(home.inside.position)
    F->>H: ghost.home.Enable(duration)
    F->>F: show eyes only (body/blue/white off)
    F->>GM: _gameEvents.GhostEaten(ghost)

    GM->>GM: points = ghost.points * ghostMultiplier
    GM->>SM: Add(points)   (200, 400, 800, 1600...)
    GM->>GM: ghostMultiplier++
    GM->>GM: OnGhostEatenEvent?.Invoke(ghost)

    Note over G,H: Eyes navigate home. GhostHome.ExitTransition<br/>returns the ghost to play after its delay.
    Note over GM: ghostMultiplier resets to 1 when the<br/>power-pellet duration timer (ResetGhostMultiplier) fires.
